                                "stop": 10.176,
                                "byte_start": 73681,
                                "byte_stop": 114432,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in 74-728, Franks against the Bowman Transportation Company will be announced by Mr. Justice Brennan."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 10.176,
                        "stop": 132.427,
